Disneyland's Main Street, waiting for the U.S. team to go by. 
</P>
<P>
	Marquis came into possession of two tickets for the final only  
last week, no small feat after the U.S. team packed stadiums in New 
Jersey, Chicago, Boston, Washington and Palo Alto, Calif. He 
decided to take his 15-year-old daughter, Brittany, because she 
plays on her high school team. And besides, he already had tickets 
