</P>
<P>
	Asked whether he could envision his daughter playing  
professionally as easy as his son, Marquis paused. 
</P>
<P>
	``Everybody always ties it to that,'' he said, ``but I'm not  
sure that's the most important thing.'' 
</P>
<P>
	He may be right. Brittany said the most important thing to her  
