	Stocks Lower; Dow Down 15.20  
</P>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks wavered today as investors cautiously  
awaited the coming flood of second-quarter earnings reports. Just 
before 3 p.m. EDT, the Dow Jones industrial average was down 15.20 
at 11,178.50. It closed at a new high of 11,193.70 on Friday. 
Several broader stock indicators were in negative territory, 
although the technology-heavy Nasdaq composite index was up 5.59 at 
2,798.66. 

