<HEADLINE> Henner Says Chicago Role Perfect </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LAS VEGAS (AP) -- Marilu Henner believes her latest role -- as the  
murderer Roxie Hart in a Las Vegas staging of the musical 
``Chicago'' -- is a perfect fit. 
</P>
<P>
	The former ``Taxi'' driver is both a native of the Windy City  
and a ``Chicago'' veteran, having played the role of Roxie 312 
times on Broadway. 
</P>
<P>
	``I've always had dancing in my blood,'' she said during a  
recent break in rehearsals. ``Once dancing's in your bones, it's in 
your bones forever.'' 
</P>
